snippet.title: Arcade Game:  Mystic Marathon (1983 Williams)
snippet.description:
A sports track & field game where you guide an elvish looking goblin in some sort of overland race.

Note sure if the colors in this game is right but you can look at the image below to see a someone playing this on an actual arcade cabinet.

http://i.ytimg.com/vi/R5OeC6Wc_yI/maxresdefault.jpg

Note: Used invincibility cheat and 1st place cheat in some of the more difficulty levels. But most of the time, throughout the later levels,  I try to play this game without using any cheats to make it look more challenging. According to MAME, this game is 99 levels and it's endless. After 99 levels, the game repeats itself over and over and the counter goes past more than 100 levels. This game could have more than 100 levels with no ending. So I'm not sure.
